{"tid":604624,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦用幾分鐘就自動熄機","createTime":"2018-03-25T01:59:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T09:31:51.000Z","uid":83936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d926f0038f1826fb3920063784abc247b3f2a0b8","tid":604624,"uid":83936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T01:59:39.000Z","msg":"1)有時入到windows用幾分鐘就自動熄機<br />\n2)有時開機個陣隔幾秒就熄跟住又開 無限loop<br />\n試過隻火牛甩哂啲線剩係駁電源線，跟住用電線駁住24pin嘅綠同黑，可以長著火牛無問題<br />\n但將24pin插入塊mb, 就有2)呢個情況<br />\n塊mb係咪換得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n塊板係asrock b85m pro4<br />\n好耐之前諗住清cpu位啲塵掃歪左幾條蝦蘇 唔知關唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04ee8c4ad64af5b1c311368407cf269a15aa68f3","tid":604624,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T02:17:02.000Z","msg":"試過差唔多情況，換咗牛就冇事<br />\n<br />\nTest 隻牛係識郁㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9439a860974a8c6e06fc87b8a618e57e2464f8ba","tid":604624,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T03:04:17.000Z","msg":"可能條ram插得唔好"},{"pid":"3724c1ced9381c6cff78a4f59088f8087cf6286f","tid":604624,"uid":173887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T09:31:51.000Z","msg":"CPU風扇係咪甩左錯位<br />\nCHECK下CPU TEMP睇下係咪過熱熄機"}]}